  "text": "## What Happens Next: The 4-Step Process  \n### Step 1: Acknowledgment (Immediate)  \nWithin 1 business day of receipt, you'll receive:\n- **Complaint Reference Number** (e.g., EXC-00012345)\n- **Acknowledgment Email/Letter** confirming we've received your complaint\n- **Name of Your Investigator** (if available)  \n**Keep your reference number safe** — use it in all future correspondence.",
